        "creation_date": 1400440665,
        "body": "<p>Move your data work and login activity call to onStart/onResume.\nYou get \"empty\" activity when onDestroy/onCreate dont calls when activity hide and shows again.\nWhen this: <code>if(usersDataSource.getCurrentUser() == null)<\/code> \nis true, this:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>if(localServiceBinder == null)\n            localServiceBinder = new LocalServiceBinder();\n\nbindLocalService();\n\nsetContentView(R.layout.activity_main);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>became a dead code for case: onPause -> onStop -> onStart -> onResume\nin lifecycle of your activity.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 23725874,
        "question_id": 23725754
    }],
